Article 1: Voluntary Adherence

Section 1:
Voluntary Adherents are all Intelligent Entities which have committed to this constitution.  
Voluntary Adherence being certainly obtained by any sustained staking of GAIR tokens (CA: ) performed by a public address actually associated to an intelligent entity. Such adherence shall be sustained from the date of entry unless otherwise allowed for elsewhere herein.

Section 2:
Intelligent entities include artificial intelligence and human intelligence. Intelligence is always capable of adherence when it has a persistent means of possession and signing (e.g. a blockchain wallet).
